channel.title: Need ideas
channel.description:
Hey, I have been making my server for a few weeks now, and have made quite a few things... eg. A rogue mini-game a skiller area (had to add some skills too) Fighter torso mini-game --Easy, just followed a tut fixed beards Made 2 lunar spells Fixed bugs ect.
But i'm just wondering what to do next... I'm pretty sure anything you tell me, i will be able to atleast try doing. I would love it if you didnt recommend the following:-
A client A web client Anything to do with rares
~~~ Sub question ~~~ I would also love someone to give me the coords for the following places
The dwarf place (think it's called kalidgram) Entrana Crandor karamja Al karid desert -- would love it to be close to the DT pyramid Tutorial island
Thanks in advance, Smitty
